reviews.text: Interesting interior for a Hong Kong style cafe, and that is all.

Have ordered lemon grass pork chop noodle soup. Completely no taste at all for the soup noodles. The pork chop was so thin. To be short, I won't come again. While my friend ordered laksa noodle soup, which was a bit better than mine but still not very tasty.
Nice place with good food.
Very small portions and slow service. Below average.
Couldn't even finish half of this dish (chef recommended).

reviews.text: 有椰子雞湯飲，海南雞肉爽帶甜，高質！
第一次試吃，無甚驚喜! 似一般茶餐廳，但較多選擇、有咖喱，海南雞飯甚至日式拉麪。初試坑烤香茅豬扒炒疍飯，味道一般，奶茶還可以的!
金牌鹽焗雞(都好食)
食物及服務一般，價格合理。
食物不错，價錢不貴
